(A system and method for controlling a cursor on a display using a trackpad input device is disclosed.) Tj
T* (Systems and methods relate to controlling a cursor on a separate display from a trackpad input device based) Tj
T* (on identified information about the motion of the trackpad input device or the computing device. The) Tj
T* (conversion factor may be determined to relate the input to the trackpad input device to controlling the cursor) Tj
T* (on the display in response to the input. The conversion factor may be adjusted when the motion information) Tj
T* (indicates that the trackpad input device or the computing device is in motion. The input signal from the input) Tj
T* (to the trackpad input device can be smoothed out by filtering out the mechanical vibration signal from the) Tj
T* (input signal. The input signal may also be smoothed by subtracting the absolute motion of the trackpad input) Tj
